Loupse,is,an,application,that,allows,users,to,remotely,control,computers,even,when,the,user,and,the,targeted,computers,are,in,separate,countries,With,Loupse,users,can,shutdown,restart,or,lock,the,screen,of,a,computer,remotely,The,app,is,still,under,development,but,API,documentation,is,already,available,Users,are,expected,to,be,able,to,access,Loupse,s,functions,from,the,website,mobile,application,or,REST,API